</center>
<P>
<blockquote>
$250 --- Coaltion Member: As an active member of SBS Coalition,
organizations will receive all the above mention benefits and
materials.<BR>

<P>
$1,000 --- Coaltion Council: As an active member of SBS Coaltion
Council, organizations will receive all above mentioned benefits
and materials, private invitations to twice-yearly policy briefings
and strategy sessions in Washington, and registration fee to the
National Small Business Summit will be waived.<BR>

<P>
$2,500 --- Coalition Founder's Circle: As an active member of
the SBS Coaltion Founder's Circle, organizations will receive
all above benefits and materials, private invitations to twice-yearly
policy briefings and stategey session in Washington, registration
fee to the National Small Business Summit waived, admission to
Founder's Circle events and receptions at yearly conference, and
monthly CEO briefing faxed to your office.<BR>

<P>
With a principled and consistent voice, the Small Business Survival
Coaltion will unify --- and amplify --- small businesses in our
nation's capitol.  Nothing less will do.
