<DOCNO>WT15-B13-44</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA034-000684-B015-461</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/sbsc/pr0922.html 204.71.237.79 19970209203641 text/html 5615
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
