<HTML>

<HEAD>

<TITLE>Requesting Hearing Transcripts and Testimonies -- TRC
</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z Beta">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>

<CENTER>
<h2>Requesting Hearing Transcripts and Testimonies</h3>
</CENTER>
<blockquote>
<P><br>
<B>Full transcripts</B> are available
for two of the Tax Reform Commission's hearings:
<UL>
<LI>The first public hearing held in <a href="/taxcom/m6-28-5.html">Washington,
D.C.</a> June 28 (with testimony from members of Congress).  
<LI>The field hearing in <a href="/taxcom/trc-802.html">Omaha</a> on August 2 (with
witnesses primarily drawn from the Midwest).
</ul>
The field hearing in south-central Los Angeles
on August 8 (featuring testimony from urban entrepreneurs) will be made available here during the week of January 15, 1996.


<P>

<P>
Copies of<B> witness testimony</B> from the TRC's
nine other public hearings are also available.  Please see the
<a href="/taxcom/schedule.html">hearing schedule</a> for dates and themes.
<P>
<U><B>To request a transcript or testimony</B></U>:
<P>
<ul>
(1) Please send a letter or fax your request to the
<a href="/taxcom/contact.html">Commission</a>.
<P>
(2) Please include your<B> name</B> and <B>address</B>
and the <B>specific hearing date</B> for which you are requesting
a transcript. 
<P>
(3) Additionally, to cover duplication costs, each
transcript and testimony costs $10.00.  Please make checks out
to <B>The Fund for the Study of Economic Growth and Tax Reform.</B>
<P>
(4)   Because of the great volume of requests for
testimony, please allow several days for the handling of your
request.  <B>If you have an urgent need for the information</B>,
you will need to call or fax in your request, then arrange a round-trip
messenger to pick up the testimony or transcripts you desire.
  We appreciate your patience.
<P>
The National Commission on Economic Growth and Tax
Reform is a non-profit, citizen group.  The $10 fee for copies
of transcripts and testimonies does not cover the full transcription
and reproduction costs for the document. <I> </I>If you are able
to make an <B>additional contribution</B> to The Fund for the
Study of Economic Growth and Tax Reform to help with the costs
associated with these transcripts and testimonies, it would be
very much appreciated by the Commission.
<P>
Thank you.
</ul>
</blockquote>
<P>
<center>[ <a href="/taxcom/">TRC Home</a> ]</center>
