<h2>THE NATIONAL COMMISSION ON ECONOMIC GROWTH AND TAX REFORM<p>
Public Hearing</h2>
<hr>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<h4>Wednesday, August 2, 1995<br>
8:00 a.m.<br>
Red Lion Hotel<br>
Grand Ballroom West<br>
Omaha, Nebraska<br></h4>
</center>
