Commission and the Congress has going forward is to
develop the trust level that when you produce the facts
and explain those, that people actually believe those,
because I think the complexity that has been brought
out of trying to go along with the IRS Code, the good
faith efforts to comply and then still get bounced
cause a huge chasm there that has to be crossed.<p>

		One of the reasons I answered Mr. Forstmann
