<html><head><title>Campus Leader</title><center><img src="cl-logo.gif"><h4>A Newsletter For Student Leaders From Young America's Foundation</h4>Volume 5, Number 1<br>
<hr><p>
<a name="contents"><h3>Contents</h3></a>
<a href="#medved">Film Critic Michael Medved Selected as 1995-96 Grover Hermann Freedom Lecturer</a><br>
<a href="#document">Document Leftist Bias on Your Campus!</a><br>
<a href="#clc">Conservative Leadership Conference to be Held in Atlanta:  November 10-11</a><br>
