<BODY background="/yaf/ground2.gif">
<h2>Cheryl C. Perry</h2>
<table align=left width="200" hspace="5">
<tr><td><img alt="Picture of Cheryl C. Perry" src="cheryl.gif">
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>Cheryl C. Perry is a program officer for Young America's Foundation, and is the assistant publisher of <I>Continuity</I>, the only conservative history journal in America.  Cheryl has been affiliated with the Foundation since 1981. </P>
<P>Prior to joining the staff of Young America's Foundation, Cheryl attended West Georgia College, and was an active member of Young Americans for Freedom in Texas.  Later, moving to Virginia, she served as YAF's financial officer.</P>
