<DOCNO>WT15-B13-142</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA034-000684-B021-311</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/heritage/mandate/ 204.71.237.79 19970209205854 text/html 3702
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 20:59:43 GMT
