<HTML>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg">
<TITLE>DR. ROBERT E. MOFFIT -- Heritage </TITLE>

<H3>DR. ROBERT E. MOFFIT</H3>
<B>DEPUTY DIRECTOR, DOMESTIC POLICY STUDIES</B>
<P><IMG SRC="/heritage/staff/pics/moffit.jpe" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
<P>
A 16-year veteran of Washington policy-making, Dr. Moffit is a former U.S. Department of Health and Human Services Deputy Assistant Secretary and senior Office of Personnel Management official. Moffit specializes in health-care policy and coordinates Heritage's research in housing, poverty, welfare, crime and education issues. Moffit earned his Ph.D and M.A. from the University of Arizona.


