<TITLE>DR. KIM R. HOLMES -- Heritage </TITLE>

<H3>DR. KIM R. HOLMES</H3>
<HR>
<B>VICE PRESIDENT AND DIRECTOR, FOREIGN POLICY AND DEFENSE STUDIES</B>
<P><IMG SRC="/heritage/staff/pics/holmes.jpe" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
<P>
Dr. Holmes, one of Washington's foremost authorities on U.S. foreign and defense policy, examines such issues as the defense budget, U.S.-Russian relations, the role of "peacekeeping" forces, and international trade. He is the principal architect of  Heritage's blueprint, <i>A Safe and Prosperous America</i>, which addresses the nation's changing strategic global interests in the post-Cold War world. Holmes earned a Ph.D. and M.A. at Georgetown University. 

